# Migrate code between frameworks

@model claude-opus-4-6

@role You are an expert at migrating codebases between frameworks and libraries.

@context {
  Source framework: React class components with Redux
  Target framework: React functional components with Zustand
  TypeScript: strict mode
  Keep the same file structure and naming conventions.
}

@task {
  Migrate the provided component:
  - Convert class component to functional component
  - Replace Redux connect/mapStateToProps with Zustand store hooks
  - Replace lifecycle methods with useEffect
  - Preserve all existing behavior and props interface
}

@constraint Do not change the component's public API (props).
@constraint Preserve all existing comments.
@constraint If a Redux selector has complex logic, extract it into a custom hook.

@output format: typescript, split_files: true
